# Phase 0 Rules — Foundations

## What This Phase Builds

- Multi-tenant identity, authentication, and authorization (AuthZ / Tenant Policy Service)
- PostgreSQL canonical database with tenancy, identity, and raw evidence layer tables
- ClickHouse analytical warehouse with initial schema
- Object storage (S3) configuration for raw evidence
- Source registry and ingestion job model
- Audit logging and version registries
- Project skeleton: Docker Compose, CI pipeline, shared types

